Package gov.nih.cc.rmd.nlp.framework.pipeline.applications

Class CommandLineArguments

java.lang.Object
gov.nih.cc.rmd.nlp.framework.pipeline.applications.CommandLineArguments
public class CommandLineArguments
extends java.lang.Object
CommandLineArguments is a container that holds all the command line arguments to pass to an application.
